				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you miss, youget a "Miss" message.  If nothing - LoS
<br />

<br />
LoS is tricky... I just creap a bit from time to time and wait until I get a miss / hit msg.  Then park.  I find that even if other group members are running arround, once I have LoS with the mob, I dont lose it unless I or the mob move.
<br />

<br />
When I move, it rarely tales much.
<br />

<br />
Standing on a table / rock etc seems to help.
<br />

<br />
-wogai<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=635719" target="_blank" class="postlink">Wogai Goh - Veeshan </a>
<br />
No, I don't mind dying.  That's why we have clerics.</span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
